    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Build Paperclip task payload.\n// NOTE: Paperclip's createIssueSchema only accepts a narrow set of fields; anything extra\n// is silently dropped. `linear_ticket_id`, `linear_issue_id`, `linear_url`, `app_id`, `labels`\n// are kept here for forward-compat / debugging (they're harmless no-ops today). The Linear ->\n// Paperclip link is actually persisted via `labelIds`, resolved by `Resolve linear label` /\n// `Capture new label ID` upstream.\nconst input = $input.first().json;\n\nconst payload = {\n  linear_ticket_id: input.issueIdentifier,\n  linear_issue_id: input.issueId,\n  linear_url: input.issueUrl,\n  app_id: input.appLabel,\n  title: input.issueTitle,\n  description: input.issueDescription,\n  labels: input.allLabels,\n  labelIds: input.linearLabelId ? [input.linearLabelId] : [],\n};\n\nreturn [{ json: { ...input, paperclipPayload: payload } }];"
      },
